@[to_additive]
theorem smul_opposite_mul {H : Subgroup G} (x g : G) (h : H.opposite) : «expr • » h (g * x) = g * «expr • » h x :=
  by
  cases h
  simp [(«expr • » · ·), mul_assoc]
